{"tid":2326573,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"粉絲注意！王嘉爾Jackson新單曲即將發佈","createTime":"2020-12-15T11:53:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T00:58:51.000Z","uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":65,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cc0fe5790d6c2793e5057563a144fc0ed9193611","tid":2326573,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T11:53:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bvU-3N7Eu1s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DbvU-3N7Eu1s&d=ZAqn3h4t0e4XfOyVRCtvGDk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=55dcb94d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bvU-3N7Eu1s</a><br />\n各位Jacky們，大哥最近要出全新華語單曲啦！（灑花轉圈加尖叫<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=413858133100604\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D413858133100604&d=ZAqn3h4t0e4XfOyVRCtvGDk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=075e34d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=413858133100604</a><br />\n光聽到這２０秒類似前導預告的釋出我就超級興奮的！！！<br />\n<br />\n去年大哥發佈個人首張全創作英文專輯《MIRRORS》，直接橫掃各大排行榜，還有今年的《Pretty Please》《100 Ways》！！這回再次以創作音樂人出發，將在12/17推出全新華語單曲《過》，眼尖的大家有沒有在影片中看到什麼亮點！<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Kb4jn6M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FKb4jn6M.jpg&h=7fe0d5e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大哥這張表情也太性感了吧！<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/q1l3jgR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fq1l3jgR.jpg&h=429c09ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不得不說，大哥身材比例超好！<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/LHp6jZg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FLHp6jZg.jpg&h=09c73dca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n是要萌死誰呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大哥在舞台上的魅力，如果以鬼滅之刃九柱來形容，絕對就是炎柱杏壽郎，既熱情又超暖！！！Jackson的火焰繼上次全創作英文專輯登上網易雲音樂數字專輯榜日榜、周榜、年榜、總榜四榜冠軍，這回就要熊熊燃燒到華語圈啦～～<br />\n期待這次的華語單曲能夠刷新紀錄！！！<br />\n<br />\n各位Jacky們！大家準備好了沒～"},{"pid":"61fb6daad5c889721fe4851f637fd399e3425920","tid":2326573,"uid":76632,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T11:57:26.000Z","msg":"似炎柱咁快d英年早逝啦。"},{"pid":"e0e5da00d0cdc3df134076c0229a334d55ed2bf6","tid":2326573,"uid":74065,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"61fb6daad5c889721fe4851f637fd399e3425920","tid":2326573,"uid":76632,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T11:57:26.000Z","msg":"似炎柱咁快d英年早逝啦。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T11:58:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/11/25/220824_14e598ba6b2d5bbd13cdb0d1e8d269f0.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F11%2F25%2F220824_14e598ba6b2d5bbd13cdb0d1e8d269f0.gif&h=a16b020e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e0efd15047d58c6111e56c8df4d0ea6b017d8ad2","tid":2326573,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T11:59:54.000Z","msg":"Dodo早已預備<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"293c2f26e1f09db68f1ad8d664acde88c5f7753f","tid":2326573,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T12:00:09.000Z","msg":"辣殺拉"},{"pid":"787aa3dec666ca7359bdd5e48aac828badbba007","tid":2326573,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T12:09:41.000Z","msg":"導ching Jackson fans?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbd4bbe86aafd19104a5fa03c3e54b3e5fd6c7a6","tid":2326573,"uid":13013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T12:10:42.000Z","msg":"屌啦第一個負評係我俾既"},{"pid":"5feb876f13b94a57accfa81b0bcd9f2d746f4b40","tid":2326573,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"787aa3dec666ca7359bdd5e48aac828badbba007","tid":2326573,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T12:09:41.000Z","msg":"導ching Jackson fans?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/